schema: %d customers id :TYP=INT;:DESC="Customer ID number";name :TYP=STR;:DESC="Customer full name";email :TYP=STR;:DESC="Customer email address";phone :TYP=STR;:DESC="Phone number as text";created :TYP=TIME;:DESC="Creation timestamp";;%d products id :TYP=INT;:DESC="Product ID number";sku :TYP=STR;:ROL=UNI;:DESC="Stock keeping unit";name :TYP=STR;:DESC="Product display name";unit_price :TYP=DEC;>=0;:DESC="Unit price, non-negative";active :TYP=BOOL;:DESC="Whether product is active";created :TYP=TIME;:DESC="Creation timestamp";;%d invoices id :TYP=INT;:DESC="Invoice ID number";customer_id :TYP=INT;:DESC="Reference to customers ID number";invoice_no :TYP=STR;:DESC="External invoice number";invoice_date :TYP=TIME;:DESC="Invoice issue date";due_date :TYP=TIME;:DESC="Payment due date";status :TYP=STR;=open,paid,overdue;:DESC="Invoice status";subtotal :TYP=DEC;>=0;:DESC="Sum of line items before tax";tax :TYP=DEC;>=0;:DESC="Tax amount";total :TYP=DEC;>=0;:DESC="Grand total";created :TYP=TIME;:DESC="Creation timestamp";;%d invoice_items id :TYP=INT;:DESC="Invoice item ID number";invoice_id :TYP=INT;:DESC="Reference to invoices ID number";product_id :TYP=INT;:DESC="Reference to products ID number";description :TYP=STR;:DESC="Line item description";quantity :TYP=INT;>0;:DESC="Quantity of product";unit_price :TYP=DEC;>=0;:DESC="Unit price at time of sale";line_total :TYP=DEC;>=0;:DESC="Quantity times unit price";;%for customers id _;invoices customer_id @;;%for products id _;invoice_items product_id @;;%for invoices id _;invoice_items invoice_id @;;
